                  "id": "L4HtyQ",
                  "name": "P1",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Pass a name and a shape to defineTable. Every value is an sz.* type; optionality, defaults and assertions are the chained methods you already know from Zod.",
