                  "name": "P2",
                  "fill": "$text-secondary",
                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "surreal-zod compiles the schema to SurrealQL DDL. The column type, the email assertion, the option<> wrapper and the default are all derived. Note fields emit ON TABLE.",
