                  "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                  "width": "fill_container",
                  "content": "Pair this with sz check, which replays every migration from zero on a throwaway database and confirms it reproduces your declared schema. Together they catch the bug every DDL tool has but few detect: a migration that no longer builds the schema it claims to.",
